{"tid":1755454,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"{警告}地區工作checklist!!!","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T15:15:53.000Z","uid":161603,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd25eb6069a319f4b27bdbfb5bbb60e171f3f9a0","tid":1755454,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家先係開始，請做好你地份工！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">實質工作</span></span><br />\n出席90%以上區議會會議<br />\n各項成功爭取（小至巴士線，修理設施道路，大至社會議題）<br />\n長期開放議員辦事處(協助填表申請政府資助etc.)<br />\n每星期最小各一次早晚街站匯報工作<br />\n於地區fb經常爆光！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">地區活動&mdash;每季1-2次</strong></span><br />\n老人探訪！！<br />\n量血壓<br />\n剪頭髮<br />\n平價義賣(柴米油鹽etc.)<br />\n本地遊(離島，米埔etc.)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">地區活動&mdash;每年1-2次</strong></span><br />\n打疫苗<br />\n影證件相<br />\n(離港旅遊團）<br />\n蛇齋餅<br />\n寫揮春<br />\n<br />\n請每日笑面迎人，明知係藍絲都要，你係代表緊我地區嘅後生仔女。你可以有性格，但吾好忘記全區人都有份出糧俾你，係你嘅客仔(我地捧得你上去，亦掉到你落返黎)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">月入三皮半吾係咁易拎的！高過d曱甴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申，居住於民主派得票數頭十，上屆踢走保皇今年成功連仼的社區。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎再加"},{"pid":"cdca35e45e9613c6f377ec97cc69301b51dc4f39","tid":1755454,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"3b9df5ca84ca5cf419c0df207db54cd011972ea9","tid":1755454,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"d2afb4788d0390efe41485d4cb927c258d37cc05","tid":1755454,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下車手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br /